{"tid":1107990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"地表最強F-15來襲  波音公布先進鷹式戰機F-15EX概念圖","createTime":"2019-04-15T15:40:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-15T18:33:27.000Z","uid":28765,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3d2d117bdebf33f4ee6cd6745ee705b6164e7f2f","tid":1107990,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T15:40:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_2759936_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_2759936_1.jpg&h=f66e59dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_2759936_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_2759936_2.jpg&h=78e15e3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國波音公司公布了新型F-15EX戰機的概念圖。（圖片來源：波音公司官網）<br />\n<br />\n2019-04-15 21:33<br />\n〔國際新聞中心／綜合報導〕美國波音公司14日在官網公布新型F-15EX先進鷹式（Advanced Eagle）戰鬥機概念圖，規劃機身改良有12個經認證的空對空和15個空對地有效負荷載點，能夠攜帶全套的空對空、空對地和海上打擊武器，容量達2萬9500磅，可以在任何特定任務中應對多個目標。<br />\n<br />\nF-15戰機在1970年代初問世，應用現代航電科技後，可以適應21世紀的作戰環境。F-15EX能補充其它機型之不足，並強化機隊的空中戰鬥能力，計劃在未來空戰中與第五代隱形戰鬥機F-22「猛禽」（F-22 Raptor）及F-35閃電（F-35 Lightening）協調作戰，進而確保美國因應目前和即將出現的威脅。<br />\n<br />\nF-15EX設計架構有助於實現新武器的集低成本、低風險之大成，電子戰方面，相關設備升級提供全方位保護，並能夠主導應對新威脅，並能和其他感測器無縫接軌，提供自動抗紅外線搜尋，增加生存率。<br />\n<br />\n先進鷹式戰機強化更大推力的引擎，並因應未來戰機的戰鬥模式，改良數位化儀表板，增強飛行員對戰場環境的理解，減少工作量負荷，使用世上最快速電腦處理器，可以處理每秒870億條指令的計算吞吐量，協助飛行員可靠的任務處理能力<br />\n<br />\n每架F-15EX戰機造價估計約8000萬美元（約台幣25億元），美國空軍已計畫購買8架F-15EX，以取代老化的F-15C/D，但這8架將建立線路費用，總價或增加到1.25億美元（約台幣39億元）。<br />\n<br />\n依據五角大廈公布的《國防戰略報告》，美國空軍每年必須增購24架戰機。而波音公司說，F-15EX是唯一能迅速迎合美國空軍的要求，而且價格又是美國空軍所能負擔得起的戰機。<br />\n<br />\n波音公司表示，在過去10年來，該公司投資了超過50億美元在技術開發上，為美國空軍帶來這款F-15戰機的最現代化版本，F-15EX戰機是最節省成本、先進和現成的解決方案，能迎合美國空軍的產能要求，並為戰機機隊增加戰力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2759936\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2759936&d=hmtFoPnP%2FIv5fOqUL3ZUatMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=18bbdccd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2759936&h=fa406736\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2759936</a>"},{"pid":"2896e7df89e088adbc7f051d1b798670a1ec0fe9","tid":1107990,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T16:00:37.000Z","msg":"又可以賣舊貨比日本同台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dcb09668b7191925213ff7a532543ba396b582a","tid":1107990,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T16:04:26.000Z","msg":"F-15可以再戰十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe3a5d8150f3dc6a100a0c36b4e36af780976239","tid":1107990,"uid":101051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T16:09:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">依據五角大廈公布的《國防戰略報告》，美國空軍每年必須增購24架戰機。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee00dba1a3f70c8bfc5c202682252f851f40a332","tid":1107990,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T16:30:37.000Z","msg":"F15夠做啦"},{"pid":"ce7398931c6868cf2c91e36c5dc4fbbd8f0dbf95","tid":1107990,"uid":68094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T16:36:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cd6fc3140d49870e149da4d2990e58742a14c9c9","tid":1107990,"uid":8949,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T16:38:12.000Z","msg":"最強超距戰終於出黎啦<br />\nf22做瞄f15做導彈軍火庫<br />\n之後都好難有其他國家拎到制空"},{"pid":"e7a7def05681d2d7da55791f2728996ec30ae38f","tid":1107990,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T16:38:12.000Z","msg":"F-35 Lightening<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f12df88ae9b3e6c4fd6218b46e59a1eb9a95f0","tid":1107990,"uid":191312,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T17:10:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://nationalinterest.org/sites/default/files/styles/desktop__1486_x_614/public/main_images/f-14tni.jpg?itok=YsGIacwx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnationalinterest.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fdesktop__1486_x_614%2Fpublic%2Fmain_images%2Ff-14tni.jpg%3Fitok%3DYsGIacwx&h=085bb6e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢架先真正係地表最強"},{"pid":"d8ddbb354fd9b8feee979f9afaee1806cf3e0636","tid":1107990,"uid":42435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T17:11:23.000Z","msg":"B52 都玩足半個世紀以上"},{"pid":"3b8b72ade56f37ea70d4a78306b4fb8c58c0c861","tid":1107990,"uid":42435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"01f12df88ae9b3e6c4fd6218b46e59a1eb9a95f0","tid":1107990,"uid":191312,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T17:10:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://nationalinterest.org/sites/default/files/styles/desktop__1486_x_614/public/main_images/f-14tni.jpg?itok=YsGIacwx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnationalinterest.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fdesktop__1486_x_614%2Fpublic%2Fmain_images%2Ff-14tni.jpg%3Fitok%3DYsGIacwx&h=085bb6e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢架先真正係地表最強"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T17:12:41.000Z","msg":"維修太貴，F18 以經做到F14 所有功能"},{"pid":"0494b21c1562aee1c36e86ca1fc52cc5b4fedad8","tid":1107990,"uid":1913